Class GeoJsonFeatureCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bremersee.geojson.GeoJsonFeatureCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class GeoJsonFeatureCollection
extends Object
implements Serializable

    A GeoJSON object with the type FeatureCollection is a feature collection object (see http://geojson.org/geojson-spec.html#feature-collection-objects ).

    Author:
    Christian Bremer

        public GeoJsonFeatureCollection(String id,
                                AbstractGeoJsonCrs crs,
                                Collection<? extends GeoJsonFeature> features,
                                boolean setBounds,
                                Map<String,Object> properties)
        Constructs a GeoJSON feature collection with the specified parameters.
        Parameters:
        id - an optional id
        crs - an optional coordinate reference system
        features - the GeoJSON features of the collection
        setBounds - if true the bounding box will be calculated otherwise the bounding box will be null
        properties - a map with named objects that are associated with the GeoJSON feature collection

      • GeoJsonFeatureCollection

                                Map<String,Object> properties)
        Constructs a GeoJSON feature collection with the specified parameters.
        Parameters:
        id - an optional id
        crsName - the name of the CRS (may be null)
        features - the GeoJSON features of the collection
        setBounds - if true the bounding box will be calculated otherwise the bounding box will be null
        properties - a map with named objects that are associated with the GeoJSON feature collection
